Justin Verlander Throws Second No-Hitter of MLB Season as Tigers Beat Jays

-- B y   N a n c y   K e r c h e v a l
-- 
2011-05-07T22:57:42Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-07/justin-verlander-throws-second-no-hitter-of-mlb-season-as-tigers-beat-jays.html
Detroit pitcher Justin Verlander threw
the second no-hitter of the Major League Baseball season in the
Tigers’ 9-0 rout of the  Toronto Blue Jays  today.  Verlander’s second career no-hitter followed Francisco
Liriano of the Minnesota Twins.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Nancy Kercheval at 
 nkercheval@bloomberg.net  